{
  "stem": "11067.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I guess it was when we were going to school, not being able to interact or play with the non-Jewish children in the area, where the parents would grab the kids and bring-- take them in, or when we were chased home from school and had stones thrown at us.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would-- I know I would run particularly-- or try and run particularly fast to get away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if I would trip and fall, I would end up coming home with a bump on the front of the head and a bump in the back from the-- from the stones, you know, being hurt.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used all the epithets that there were normally, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dirty Jew and, sort of, we don't want you here type of things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Specifically, I don't think I, you know, know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was the epithets that are used all the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you, you, you-- yeah, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what's the-- what was the explanation?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, you're Jewish, and they don't want anything to do with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Trying to go into the stores and buying things, food or other articles, was also a difficult thing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you realized there and then that you were persona non grata.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't want to sell to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the same happened, of course, the boycotting of our own store, where they would come at night and write 'Dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't buy here' in-- in big red letters in front of the store that my father, in the middle of the night, then would go out and scrub off.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was, it was very evident.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There wasn't-- childhood sort of melted away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You grew up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You-- you realized that you, that you had to take responsibility, I guess.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
